text.tspan: Place a piece in an empty square
1. JUMP over at least one piece to an empty square
2. Remove any pieces on the squares passed over
3. Score POINTS to the sum of the VALUES of the removed pieces
Move the piece in a straight line orthogonally or diagonally
so that it passes over any number of squares up to its VALUE
and lands on the following square
Player with most total POINTS wins
